    public class BindingInfo

    data that describes a single databinding expression. This data is put together during an analysis pass, then used for codegen.

      • BindingInfo

        public BindingInfo(IMXMLBindingNode bindingNode,
           int index,
           MXMLClassDirectiveProcessor host,
           boolean reverseSourceAndDest)
        Constructor for use with a BindingNode. The binding node specifies both the source and destination expressions explicitly. Usually these come from either the tag, or as an implementation detail of the tag
        Parameters:
        reverseSourceAndDest - - if true, analyze the binding as if the source was the destination and the destination was the source
